      "text": "[[Liquid Democracy]] is in many ways one such mashup. It took elements of social networks, markets, and threw in some mathematics regarding reputation and resilience. It asked what would happen to conversation if we allowed votes to flow through the network, and looked to create structures which would progressively incentivise deeper and richer local conversations.\n\n"
